text: KJMX (99.5 FM, "The Rock 99.5") is a radio station broadcasting a classic rock music format. Licensed to Reedsport, Oregon, United States, the station is currently owned by Bicoastal Media Licenses III, LLC, and features programming from Westwood One. ==References== ==External links== * JMX Category:Classic rock radio stations in the United States Category:Douglas County, Oregon Category:Radio stations established in 1993 Category:1993 establishments in Oregon
